headline: How Investors May Respond To United Parcel Service (UPS) Customs Delays and Service Guarantee Suspension
summary: In recent days, United Parcel Service (UPS) has faced significant operational challenges due to the end of the de minimis exemption for international parcels entering the US, causing customs clearance delays and a backlog of packages, as well as the suspension of its money-back Service Guarantee for international shipments. These disruptions have heightened customer frustration, with some shipments at risk of destruction and operational risks for UPS increasing. Operational breakdown related...
